---
// src/components/Reviews.astro
---
<section id="reviews" class="section-mid py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">

    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-5">
        <span class="w-8 h-px bg-amber-400/40"></span>
        <span class="font-body text-amber-500 text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase">Your Voice</span>
        <span class="w-8 h-px bg-amber-400/40"></span>
      </div>
      <span class="gold-line mx-auto"></span>
      <h2 class="section-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-white">Customer <span class="text-amber-400">Reviews</span></h2>
      <p class="font-body text-gray-500 mt-4 max-w-lg mx-auto text-sm sm:text-base">
        Share your experience – the good, the vibes, the magic.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Review Form -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <form id="review-form" class="contact-card card-lift rounded-2xl p-7 space-y-5">
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-white font-bold">Leave a Review</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" class="bg-night-800 border border-amber-400/20 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-gray-200 placeholder-gray-600 focus:outline-none focus:border-amber-400/50 w-full" required />
          <input type="email" placeholder="Email (won't be shown)" class="bg-night-800 border border-amber-400/20 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-gray-200 placeholder-gray-600 focus:outline-none focus:border-amber-400/50 w-full" />
        </div>
        <textarea placeholder="Your review..." rows="4" class="bg-night-800 border border-amber-400/20 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-gray-200 placeholder-gray-600 focus:outline-none focus:border-amber-400/50 w-full" required></textarea>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-gold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-body text-sm tracking-wide w-full sm:w-auto">Submit Review</button>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">Your email is private. We'll never share it.</p>
      </form>
    </div>

    <!-- Sample Reviews -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="event-card card-lift rounded-2xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-amber-400/20 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-400 font-bold">T</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-body text-white font-medium">Thando M.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">2 weeks ago</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">"Best amapiano vibes in Mdantsane! The DJ set on Friday was pure fire. The cocktail menu is dangerous – in a good way."</p>
        <div class="mt-3 flex gap-1 text-amber-400">★★★★★</div>
      </div>

      <div class="event-card card-lift rounded-2xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-amber-400/20 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-400 font-bold">S</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-body text-white font-medium">Sipho K.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">1 month ago</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">"I booked a table for my birthday and the staff went above and beyond. The private area was lit. Definitely coming back!"</p>
        <div class="mt-3 flex gap-1 text-amber-400">★★★★★</div>
      </div>

      <div class="event-card card-lift rounded-2xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-amber-400/20 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-400 font-bold">L</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-body text-white font-medium">Lindiwe N.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">3 weeks ago</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">"Sundays are now my favourite day. Umlilo Sundays is a whole mood. The braai combo is worth every cent."</p>
        <div class="mt-3 flex gap-1 text-amber-400">★★★★☆</div>
      </div>

      <div class="event-card card-lift rounded-2xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-amber-400/20 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-400 font-bold">B</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-body text-white font-medium">Bongani Z.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">1 week ago</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">"The butchery is a game changer! Grabbed some T-bone steaks and they were top quality. The eKoneni marinade is something else."</p>
        <div class="mt-3 flex gap-1 text-amber-400">★★★★★</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-8">
      <button id="load-more-reviews" class="btn-outline px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-body text-sm tracking-wide">Load More Reviews</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  // Prevent form submission (static demo)
  document.getElementById('review-form').addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    alert('Thank you for your review! (This is a demo – not actually submitted)');
  });

  // Load more is just a placeholder
  document.getElementById('load-more-reviews').addEventListener('click', () => {
    alert('More reviews coming soon!');
  });
</script>